      "assessmentDate": "2026-03-20T00:00:00Z",
      "couMismatchNote": "Comparator dataset acquired under steady-state constant-flow conditions; COU requires pulsatile flow validation. Mismatch explicitly acknowledged in PTR-CPB-2024-07 Section 4.3 but not reflected in factor scoring."
    }
